    "dualManifest": "YES. One component root (loom-nucleus/) carries sibling .codex-plugin/plugin.json and .claude-plugin/plugin.json over shared skills/, agents/, hooks/ (design 2.1). Codex consumes skills + hooks; Claude additionally consumes agents.",
